description: Demolition of existing petrol filling station (sui generis); erection of 9-storey mixed-use building for use as purpose built student accommodation (sui generis) with units on upper floors and ancillary accommodation on ground floor along with 1 flexible ground floor unit (Classes E(d), F1(a, b d & e) and F2(b)), residents' lobby, study areas, laundry room, multifunction spaces and cycle parking, external amenity terrace, short-term cycle parking, landscaping and associated works.
